'''彼得·麦凯''' {{post-nominals|country=CAN|PC|QC}}（{{lang|en|Peter Gordon MacKay}}，{{bd|1965年|9月27日|||catIdx=MacKay, Peter}}），[[加拿大|加拿大]]政治人物和律師，1997年至2015年間曾任[[加拿大國會下議院|加拿大國會下議院]]議員，並曾於[[加拿大保守黨|加拿大保守黨]]執政期間先後出任外交部長（2006年-2007年）、國防部長（2007年-2013年）和司法部長（2013年-2015年）等[[加拿大内閣|聯邦内閣]]要職。他亦是[[加拿大进步保守党|加拿大进步保守党]]的最后一任黨魁；他於2003年促成該黨與[[加拿大聯盟|加拿大聯盟]]合并为現有的加拿大保守黨。

== 早年生活 ==

彼得·麦凯生于[[新斯科舍省|新斯科舍省]][[新格拉斯哥|新格拉斯哥]]，父親艾爾默（{{lang|en|Elmer MacKay}}）為一林木商人和律師，並曾於1970至90年代以[[加拿大進步保守黨|加拿大進步保守黨]]黨員身份擔任[[加拿大國會下議院|加拿大國會下議院]]{{le|中諾華|Central Nova}}選區議員和聯邦内閣部長<ref name="CBC150529">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/peter-mackay-cites-love-for-my-family-as-he-bows-out-of-federal-politics-1.3092480 |title=Peter MacKay cites 'love for my family' as he bows out of federal politics |publisher=CBC News |first=Janyce |last=McGregor |accessdate=2015-11-06 |date=2015-05-29 |archive-date=2021-06-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210627235204/https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/peter-mackay-cites-love-for-my-family-as-he-bows-out-of-federal-politics-1.3092480 }}</ref>。母親艾琳（{{lang|en|Eirene Macha MacKay}}）則為一心理學家，其祖先包括{{le|第三代卡里冬伯爵詹姆斯·亞歷山大|James Alexander, 3rd Earl of Caledon}}和{{le|第一代維魯拉姆伯爵詹姆斯·格里姆斯頓|James Grimston, 1st Earl of Verulam}}<ref>{{cite web |author=John Demont |url=http://www.macleans.ca/article.jsp?content=20030526_59817_59817 |title=THE ROAD TO RELEVANCE | Macleans.ca — Canada — Features |publisher=Macleans.ca |date=May 26, 2003 |accessdate=May 5, 2011 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110807100144/http://www.macleans.ca/article.jsp?content=20030526_59817_59817 |archivedate=2011年8月7日 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Ottawa |first=The |url=http://www.canada.com/ottawacitizen/news/story.html?id=1f41e020-a6e7-4313-bfe9-955b2017c2a3 |title=Royal Navy Cmdr. Bredin Delap is the father of Peter MacKay's mother, Macha |publisher=Canada.com |date=June 16, 2008 |accessdate=May 5, 2011 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121108205319/http://www.canada.com/ottawacitizen/news/story.html?id=1f41e020-a6e7-4313-bfe9-955b2017c2a3 |archivedate=2012年11月8日 }}</ref><ref name=parlg1>{{cite book|last=Normandin|first=A.L.|author2=Pierre G. Normandin|title=The Canadian parliamentary guide|publisher=Normandin|year=1974|page=285|quote=M. July 15, 1961 to dau. of Commander Bradin Delap of Centreville, Kings County, NS; Four children: Cethlyn Laura, Peter Gordon, Sheila Mary Louise and Andrew.}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://thepeerage.com/p19926.htm#i199257 |title=Ancestry of Commander Bredin Delap1 |publisher=Thepeerage.com |accessdate=May 5, 2011 |archive-date=2021-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210615165302/https://thepeerage.com/p19926.htm#i199257 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=6m4-AQAAIAAJ&q=Eirene+Macha+Delap&dq=Eirene+Macha+Delap&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0CBsQ6AEwAWoVChMIy_K-3ejQyAIVhKoeCh2tggTj |title=存档副本 |access-date=2015-11-06 |archive-date=2019-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190609052848/https://books.google.ca/books?id=6m4-AQAAIAAJ&q=Eirene+Macha+Delap&dq=Eirene+Macha+Delap&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0CBsQ6AEwAWoVChMIy_K-3ejQyAIVhKoeCh2tggTj |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

麥凱與家人在沃爾夫維爾（{{lang|en|Wolfville}}）成長，從格林尼治（{{lang|en|Greenwich}}）的霍爾頓中學畢業後到{{le|阿卡迪亞大學|Acadia University}}修讀，1987年獲得文學士學位後再到[[達爾豪西大學|達爾豪西大學]]修讀法律，於1990年畢業<ref name="Citizen150530">{{cite news |url=http://ottawacitizen.com/news/national/peter-mckay-leaving-politics-reports |title=Peter MacKay's exit takes another 'progressive' out of Tory caucus |publisher=《渥太華公民報》 |first=Jason |last=Fekete |accessdate=2015-11-06 |date=2015-05-30 |archive-date=2019-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190629084339/https://ottawacitizen.com/news/national/peter-mckay-leaving-politics-reports }}</ref>並於1991年6月獲取新斯科舍律師資格<ref name="bio">{{cite web |url=http://www.petermackay.ca/meet_peter.php |title=Peter MacKay ~ Representing Central Nova |publisher=Petermackay.ca |accessdate=2015-11-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150620052956/http://petermackay.ca/meet_peter.php |archivedate=2015-06-20 }}</ref>。他曾在德資鋼鐵及軍工生產商[[蒂森克虜伯|蒂森]]工作<ref name="CBC150529"/>，到1993年則被委任為新斯科舍省中部檢控官<ref name="Citizen150530"/><ref name="bio"/>。

== 從政 ==
=== 初進國會 ===
麥凱於1997年聯邦大選中代表[[加拿大進步保守黨|加拿大進步保守黨]]角逐新斯科舍省東北部的{{le|皮克圖-安蒂戈尼什-蓋斯伯勒|Pictou—Antigonish—Guysborough}}選區議席，並以42%得票率當選，首度晉身[[加拿大國會下議院|國會下議院]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.herald.ns.ca/fedelect97/97archive/jun3/970603102.html|title=MacKay carries on family tradition|work=The Chronicle Herald|date=June 3, 1997|accessdate=September 29, 2014|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20011130174850/http://www.herald.ns.ca/fedelect97/97archive/jun3/970603102.html|archivedate=2001年11月30日|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。他隨之獲任為進步保守黨在下議院的首席議員，並在下議院的司法與人權常務委員會中代表該黨<ref name="parlroles">{{cite web|url=http://www.parl.gc.ca/Parliamentarians/en/members/Peter-Gordon-MacKay(82)/Roles|title=The Honourable Peter Gordon MacKay: Roles|publisher=加拿大國會下議院|accessdate=2015-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160111013939/http://www.parl.gc.ca/Parliamentarians/en/members/Peter-Gordon-MacKay(82)/Roles|archive-date=2016-01-11|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。他再於2000年聯邦大選中在該選區連任<ref name="parlroles"/>。

=== 進步保守黨黨魁 ===
[[喬·克拉克|喬·克拉克]]於2002年8月宣佈辭去進步保守黨黨魁職位<ref name="CBC050503">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news2/background/conservativeparty/pcparty.html |title=CBC News Indepth: The Conservative Party |publisher=CBC News |accessdate=2015-11-06 |date=2005-05-03 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305153354/http://www.cbc.ca/news2/background/conservativeparty/pcparty.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而麥凱則於2003年1月宣佈角逐該職，並被視為熱門人選<ref name="CBC030116">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/nova-scotia/mackay-to-run-for-tory-leadership-1.390588 |title=MacKay to run for Tory leadership |publisher=CBC News |accessdate=2015-11-06 |date=2003-01-16 |archive-date=2021-11-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211119161159/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/nova-scotia/mackay-to-run-for-tory-leadership-1.390588 }}</ref><ref name="HP150529">{{cite news |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.ca/2015/05/29/profile-mackays-colourf_n_7470104.html |title=A Look At MacKay's Career Beyond The 6 'Sexiest Male MP' Titles |publisher=加新社 |work=《[[哈芬登郵報|哈芬登郵報]]》加拿大版 |first=Bruce |last=Cheadle |accessdate=2015-11-06 |date=2015-05-29 |archive-date=2019-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190629012809/https://www.huffingtonpost.ca/2015/05/29/profile-mackays-colourf_n_7470104.html }}</ref>。在同年5月31日舉行的進步保守黨黨魁選舉中，麥凱在每輪投票中皆領先其他候選人，到第四輪投票以64%對36%得票率擊敗僅餘對手[[彭迪思|彭迪思]]而告當選<ref name="CBC030601">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/new-tory-leader-mackay-calls-for-unity-1.358876 |title=New Tory leader MacKay calls for unity |publisher=CBC News |accessdate=2015-11-06 |date=2003-06-01 |archive-date=2016-02-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160207104801/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/new-tory-leader-mackay-calls-for-unity-1.358876 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在第三輪投票中得票最少而被淘汰的{{le|大衛·奧查德|David Orchard}}在第四輪投票舉行前與麥凱會面，兩人並達成協議，奧查德隨後呼籲支持者在第四輪投票中支持麥凱，這成為麥凱的致勝關鍵<ref name="CBC030601"/>。奧查德和麥凱之間的協議内容後來曝光，當中包括麥凱承諾不會安排進步保守黨與[[加拿大聯盟|加拿大聯盟]]合併<ref name="CBC050503"/><ref name="HP150529"/><ref name="CPAC131016">{{cite web |url=http://www.cpac.ca/en/highlight/the-conservative-merger-10-years-later/ |title=The Conservative Merger: 10 Years Later |publisher=CPAC |accessdate=2015-11-06 |date=2013-10-16 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304104003/http://www.cpac.ca/en/highlight/the-conservative-merger-10-years-later/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

然而，兩黨高層卻在往後數個月内就合併事宜磋商<ref name="CBC031009">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/alliance-pc-merger-talks-reach-critical-point-1.366247 |title=Alliance, PC merger talks reach critical point |publisher=CBC News |accessdate=2015-11-06 |date=2003-10-09 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305225136/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/alliance-pc-merger-talks-reach-critical-point-1.366247 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而麥凱亦於2003年10月16日與加拿大聯盟黨魁[[斯蒂芬·哈珀|斯蒂芬·哈珀]]共同宣佈達成協議，將兩黨合併成新的[[加拿大保守黨|加拿大保守黨]]<ref name="CBC031016">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/harper-and-mackay-announce-deal-to-unite-the-right-1.391784 |title=Harper and MacKay announce deal to unite the right |publisher=CBC News |accessdate=2015-11-06 |date=2003-10-16 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305153348/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/harper-and-mackay-announce-deal-to-unite-the-right-1.391784 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。部分進步保守黨黨員不滿兩黨合併，更指麥凱為「叛徒」（{{lang|en|"traitor"}}）<ref name="CBC031025">{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/protesters-call-mackay-traitor-1.362583 |title=Protesters call MacKay 'traitor' |publisher=CBC News |accessdate=2015-11-06 |date=2003-10-25 }}</ref><ref name="CBC031031">{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/mackay-faces-anti-merger-demonstrators-1.405532 |title=MacKay faces anti-merger demonstrators |publisher=CBC News |accessdate=2015-11-06 |date=2003-10-31 }}</ref>，但這項合併於同年12月6日獲90%的進步保守黨代表投票支持<ref name="CBC060202">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news2/background/conservativeparty/uniteright_timeline.html |title=Unite the right: Timeline |publisher=CBC News |accessdate=2015-11-06 |date=2006-02-02 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305225130/http://www.cbc.ca/news2/background/conservativeparty/uniteright_timeline.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而加拿大保守黨亦於同月8日正式登記成立<ref name="CBC031216">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/conservative-party-unveils-new-logo-1.406118 |title=Conservative party unveils new logo |publisher=CBC News |accessdate=2015-11-06 |date=2003-12-16 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305153351/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/conservative-party-unveils-new-logo-1.406118 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，麥凱遂成為進步保守黨的末任黨魁。

=== 保守黨副黨魁 ===
麥凱最初表示有意競逐保守黨黨魁<ref name="CBC031216"/>，但於2004年1月宣佈放棄此念頭，指當時距他當選進步保守黨黨魁只得七個月，自己的財務不足以應付另一次黨魁選舉的競選工程<ref name="CBC040113">{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/mackay-won-t-run-to-lead-new-party-1.518553 |title=MacKay won't run to lead new party |publisher=CBC News |accessdate=2015-11-06 |date=2004-01-13 }}</ref>。哈珀於同年3月舉行的黨魁選舉中當選保守黨黨魁，並委任麥凱為該黨的副黨魁<ref name="CPAC131016"/><ref name="CPAC040320">{{cite web |url=http://www.cpac.ca/en/2004-conservative-leadership/ |title=2004 Conservative Leadership Convention |publisher=CPAC |accessdate=2015-11-06 |date=2004-03-20 |archive-date=2022-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220327083808/https://www.cpac.ca/en/2004-conservative-leadership/ }}</ref>。

麥凱在2004年6月舉行的[[2004年加拿大國會下議院選舉|聯邦大選]]中代表保守黨出戰重組而成的{{le|中諾華|Central Nova}}選區，並贏取該議席重返下議院<ref name="parlroles"/><ref name="CBCvote08CentralNova">{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news2/canadavotes/riding/013/ |title=Central Nova - Canada Votes |publisher=CBC News |accessdate=2015-11-06 }}</ref>。保守黨在這次選舉成為[[官方反對黨|官方反對黨]]，而麥凱則獲哈珀委任為該黨的公共安全及應急準備事務評議員，成為[[影子内閣|影子内閣]]一員<ref name="CBC040722">{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/mackay-reynolds-key-in-tory-shadow-cabinet-1.476722 |title=MacKay, Reynolds key in Tory shadow cabinet |publisher=CBC News |accessdate=2015-11-06 |date=2004-07-22 }}</ref>。

以少數姿態執政的[[加拿大自由黨|自由黨]]政府於2005年末倒台，觸發2006年聯邦大選。麥凱在中諾華選區順利連任<ref name="parlroles"/><ref name="CBCvote08CentralNova"/>，而隨著保守黨贏取少數政府，麥凱亦被邀[[加拿大内閣|入閣]]<ref name="Citizen150530"/>。

=== 聯邦内閣部長 ===
[[File:MacKay_et_Rice.jpg|thumb]]會面（2006年）]]
保守黨在2006年大選獲得執政地位後，新任[[加拿大總理|總理]]哈珀委任麥凱為聯邦外交部長和加拿大海洋省份商機部長；2007年中則調任國防部長<ref name="parlroles"/>。麥凱在[[2008年加拿大國會下議院選舉|2008年]]和[[2011年加拿大國會下議院選舉|2011年聯邦大選]]中連任中諾華選區國會議員，並在保守黨政府中留任國防部長<ref name="parlroles"/>。

2010年7月，麥凱在[[紐芬蘭島|紐芬蘭島]]中部一釣魚營地休假期間獲加拿大軍方派遣直升機接載前往[[甘德_(紐芬蘭-拉布拉多)|甘德]]機場，在當地轉乘加拿大政府專機前往安大略省[[倫敦_(加拿大)|倫敦市]]出席一項聯邦政府宣傳活動<ref name="CBC111202">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/mackay-s-helicopter-story-doesn-t-fly-mps-say-1.1121363 |title=MacKay's helicopter story doesn't fly, MPs say |publisher=CBC News |accessdate=2015-11-27 |date=2011-12-02 |archive-date=2021-11-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211120035815/https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/mackay-s-helicopter-story-doesn-t-fly-mps-say-1.1121363 }}</ref>。從釣魚營地前往甘德機場的直升機行程耗費1萬6千元，並被解釋為讓麥凱考察軍方的搜救演集<ref name="NP130128">{{cite news|url=http://news.nationalpost.com/news/canada/dnd-emails-reveal-new-questions-over-peter-mackays-cormorant-helicopter-ride-to-news-conference |title=DND emails reveal new questions over Peter MacKay's Cormorant helicopter ride to news conference |publisher=''National Post'' |first=Lee |last=Berthiaume |accessdate=2015-11-27 |date=2013-01-28 }}</ref>。事件於2011年9月被揭發後，麥凱被指濫用政府資源<ref name="NP130128"/>。

麥凱和另外兩名内閣部長於2010年7月出席另一場宣傳活動，宣佈加拿大政府有意購買65部[[F-35閃電II戰鬥機|F-35閃電II戰鬥機]]，並坐在該戰機模型的駕駛艙讓媒體拍照。在自由黨國防事務評議員的質詢下，麥凱以書面回應該項宣傳活動耗費4萬7千元，而戰機模型則由生產商[[洛克希德·馬丁|-{zh-hans:洛克希德·马丁;zh-hk:洛歇·馬田;zh-tw:洛歇·馬丁;}-]]免費提供；此舉再被國會反對黨議員詬病<ref name="CBC120605">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/f-35-photo-op-47k-minister-in-pilot-s-seat-priceless-1.1182431 |title=F-35 photo op: $47K. Minister in pilot's seat: priceless |publisher=加新社 |work=CBC News |accessdate=2015-11-27 |date=2012-06-05 |archive-date=2021-11-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211122064335/https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/f-35-photo-op-47k-minister-in-pilot-s-seat-priceless-1.1182431 }}</ref>。

哈珀於2013年7月15日改組内閣，麥凱調任司法部長<ref name="CBC130715">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/harper-adds-8-new-faces-in-major-cabinet-shakeup-1.1307385 |title=Harper adds 8 new faces in major cabinet shakeup |publisher=CBC News |first=Kathleen |last=Harris |accessdate=2015-11-27 |date=2013-07-15 |archive-date=2021-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211128010856/https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/harper-adds-8-new-faces-in-major-cabinet-shakeup-1.1307385 }}</ref>。

=== 離開政壇 ===
2015年5月29日，麥凱在[[新斯科舍省|新斯科舍省]]宣佈不會在[[2015年加拿大國會下議院選舉|同年聯邦大選]]中尋求連任，以便陪伴家人，但留任中諾華選區國會議員和司法部長至大選為止，並不排除日後重返政壇<ref name="CBC150529"/><ref name="HP150529"/><ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.singtao.ca/vancouver/2015-05-30/headline1432978337d5604461.html |title=馬逵退出政壇 哈珀再失主將 |publisher=《[[星島日報|星島日報]]》加西版 |accessdate=2015-11-28 |date=2015-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208094658/http://news.singtao.ca/vancouver/2015-05-30/headline1432978337d5604461.html |archive-date=2015-12-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。他於2016年2月加入位於[[多倫多|多倫多]]的貝克與麥肯齊律師事務所（{{lang|en|Baker & McKenzie}}），成為該行的合夥人<ref name="CBC160125">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/nova-scotia/peter-mackay-toronto-law-firm-partner-baker-mckenzie-1.3418382 |title=Peter MacKay joins law firm Baker & McKenzie as a partner |publisher=CBC News |accessdate=2016-02-05 |date=2016-01-25 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108114717/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/nova-scotia/peter-mackay-toronto-law-firm-partner-baker-mckenzie-1.3418382 }}</ref>。

保守黨於2015年聯邦大選失去執政地位後，哈珀辭任黨魁，麥凱隨即被視為接任黨魁的熱門人選<ref name="CBC160118">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/grenier-oleary-conservative-poll-1.3408600 |title=Kevin O'Leary and Peter MacKay top Tory leadership poll |first=Éric |last=Grenier |publisher=CBC News |accessdate=2016-09-15 |date=2016-01-18 |archive-date=2022-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220324182607/https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/grenier-oleary-conservative-poll-1.3408600 }}</ref>。然而，他於2016年9月宣佈以陪伴家人為由而無意參選黨魁<ref name="CTV160912">{{cite news |url=http://www.ctvnews.ca/politics/peter-mackay-won-t-seek-conservative-leadership-1.3068919 |title=Peter MacKay won't seek Conservative leadership |first=Laura |last=Payton |publisher=CTV News |accessdate=2016-09-15 |date=2016-09-12 |archive-date=2020-02-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200224024322/https://www.ctvnews.ca/politics/peter-mackay-won-t-seek-conservative-leadership-1.3068919 }}</ref>。

[[2019年加拿大聯邦大選|2019年聯邦大選]]前夕，《[[環球郵報|環球郵報]]》報道指麥凱支持者已作準備，若由[[安德魯·熙爾|熙爾]]領導的保守黨未能贏取大選的話，便可為麥凱啟動程序競選黨魁。就此麥凱回應指他本人並不瞭解有關舉動，又稱自己歇盡所能在大選中協助和支持熙爾及其團隊<ref>{{Cite news|title=Allies of former Conservative Party minister Peter MacKay mull leadership bid|url=https://www.theglobeandmail.com/politics/article-allies-of-former-conservative-minister-peter-mackay-mull-leadership/|access-date=2019-10-11|archive-date=2022-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220427060821/https://www.theglobeandmail.com/politics/article-allies-of-former-conservative-minister-peter-mackay-mull-leadership/}}</ref>。保守黨在該屆大選中再度敗予[[加拿大自由黨|自由黨]]，面臨黨內壓力的熙爾於同年末宣布辭任黨魁<ref>{{cite web |title=Canada Conservative leader in surprise resignation |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-50762474 |website=BBC News |date=12 December 2019 |accessdate=2020-08-25 |archive-date=2020-06-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200624103218/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-50762474 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Rabson |first1=Mia |first2= |title=Conservative party in disarray over Scheer private school controversy |url=https://www.nationalobserver.com/2019/12/15/news/conservative-party-disarray-over-scheer-private-school-controversy |website=National Observer |language=en |date=15 December 2019 |accessdate=2020-08-25 |archive-date=2020-06-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200624010441/https://www.nationalobserver.com/2019/12/15/news/conservative-party-disarray-over-scheer-private-school-controversy |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=MacCharles |first1=Tonda |title=Andrew Scheer quitting as Conservative leader amid controversy |url=https://www.thestar.com/politics/federal/2019/12/12/andrew-scheer-to-step-down-as-conservative-party-leader.html |website=thestar.com |language=en |date=12 December 2019 |accessdate=2020-08-25 |archive-date=2020-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806043149/https://www.thestar.com/politics/federal/2019/12/12/andrew-scheer-to-step-down-as-conservative-party-leader.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但留任至新任黨魁當選為止<ref>{{cite web |last1=Connolly |first1=Amanda |title=Conservative Leader Andrew Scheer resigns, vows to stay on until new leader chosen |url=https://globalnews.ca/news/6288286/andrew-scheer-resignation/ |website=Global News |accessdate=2020-08-25 |archive-date=2020-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925195209/https://globalnews.ca/news/6288286/andrew-scheer-resignation/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2020年1月15日，麥凱在[[推特|推特]]發文宣布參選保守黨黨魁<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=I'm in. Stay tuned.|url=https://twitter.com/PeterMacKay/status/1217527351518679042|last=MacKay|first=Peter|date=2020-01-15|website=@PeterMacKay|language=en|access-date=2020-01-17|archive-date=2022-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220310184308/https://twitter.com/PeterMacKay/status/1217527351518679042}}</ref>。在同年8月舉行的黨魁選舉中，麥凱不敵[[艾林·奧圖爾|艾林·奧圖爾]]<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-08-23|title=Erin O'Toole wins Conservative Party of Canada leadership on 3rd ballot|url=https://www.cp24.com/news/erin-o-toole-wins-conservative-party-of-canada-leadership-on-3rd-ballot-1.5075658|access-date=2020-08-24|website=CP24|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205125451/https://www.cp24.com/news/good-morning-i-m-erin-o-toole-new-tory-leader-wins-after-hours-long-delay-1.5075658|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 個人生活 ==
麥凱於2012年與娜扎寧·阿夫信-賈姆（Nazanin Afshin-Jam）結婚<ref name="CBC150529"/>。她來自伊朗，2003年獲[[世界小姐|世界小姐]]加拿大冠軍，同年代表加拿大參與世界小姐競選並獲亞軍<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2003-12-07/irish-miss-world-begins-reign/101852 |title=Irish Miss World begins reign |publisher=ABC News |accessdate=2015-11-28 |date=2003-12-07 |archive-date=2022-05-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220503011429/https://www.abc.net.au/news/2003-12-07/irish-miss-world-begins-reign/101852 }}</ref>。她其後成立人權組織「停止處決兒童」（{{lang|en|Stop Child Executions}}），目的為爭取伊朗政府終止向未成年罪犯判處死刑<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/politics/ottawa-notebook/peter-mackay-weds-rights-activist-former-beauty-queen/article620485/06/ |title=Peter MacKay weds rights activist, former beauty queen |publisher=《[[環球郵報|環球郵報]]》 |first=Gloria |last=Galloway |accessdate=2015-05-24 |date=2012-01-04 |archive-date=2017-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170303013851/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/politics/ottawa-notebook/peter-mackay-weds-rights-activist-former-beauty-queen/article620485/06/ }}</ref>。兩人育有一子一女<ref>{{cite news |url=http://thechronicleherald.ca/novascotia/1314102-peter-mackay-and-nazanin-afshin-jam-announce-birth-of-baby-girl-valentia |title=Peter MacKay and Nazanin Afshin-Jam announce birth of baby girl Valentia |publisher=''The Chronicle Herald'' |first=Andrea |last=Gunn |accessdate=2015-11-28 |date=2015-09-30 |archive-date=2018-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180714135403/http://thechronicleherald.ca/novascotia/1314102-peter-mackay-and-nazanin-afshin-jam-announce-birth-of-baby-girl-valentia }}</ref>。

